{"tid":658612,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"日本電視節目教學 1分鐘學識極速殺蚊方法","createTime":"2018-05-09T06:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T06:49:52.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2274e95b9efb1a2555c4277879a3c0245bf0845c","tid":658612,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T06:39:07.000Z","msg":"夏天正式來臨，除了天氣愈來愈熱外，最令人懊惱的問題離不開蚊患。每次有蚊出現時，相信大家也想極速消滅牠們，不過有否發現怎也拍不到牠們？日本電視節目《月曜から夜ふかし》，最近近便介紹了正確打蚊方法，而且更1分鐘學懂！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/nm_fb_mosquito_feature_17191667265aec4efdcb670.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2Fnm_fb_mosquito_feature_17191667265aec4efdcb670.jpg&h=c31ffff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nmplus.hk/lifestyle/殺蚊-蚊-教學-夏天/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmplus.hk%2Flifestyle%2F%E6%AE%BA%E8%9A%8A-%E8%9A%8A-%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8-%E5%A4%8F%E5%A4%A9%2F&d=tXfh0r%2FUpTK3OaQPDnQbR%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=786ec5b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nmplus.hk/lifestyle/殺蚊-蚊-教學-夏天/</a>"},{"pid":"aaf6ec9e738477abd5f8623954f172a15681c9da","tid":658612,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T06:42:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1分鐘學識極速殺蚊方法</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一般人看見蚊子時，通常會嘗試徒手捉、雙手由左至右向內拍，有些人甚至先讓蚊吸自己的血，在牠停留的時候拍死牠。以上的方法，其實也是錯誤的。最近日本電視節目《月曜から夜ふかし》便介紹了正確打蚊方法，原來打蚊時，雙手要由上、下方拍。原因是蚊子上下移動的速度較快，而左右移動的速度相對較慢，所以若雙手從上、下而來，大大提高擊中率。方法原來這麼簡單，大家要記得了！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/20180205115232_5a77d50066e6a_13179618765aec46cf64eec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F20180205115232_5a77d50066e6a_13179618765aec46cf64eec.jpg&h=d2e9a713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">雙手由左至右向內拍屬錯誤方法</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/20180205115311_5a77d527ac47e_20739137255aec47090c4bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F20180205115311_5a77d527ac47e_20739137255aec47090c4bd.jpg&h=654f94d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">先讓蚊吸自己的血，在牠停留的時候拍死牠當然是錯誤方法</span></div>"},{"pid":"638a485a5ccc6090b06b013bfa2cc1a445582abc","tid":658612,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T06:45:12.000Z","msg":"上下好難就喎<br />\n<br />\n加上要先郁其中一隻手向上過隻蚊先<br />\n<br />\n隻蚊隨時飛走左"},{"pid":"09014f49f44690cfb7f9c8299a2a4fbc863eb201","tid":658612,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T06:46:46.000Z","msg":"我單手都得啦"},{"pid":"8bff4fea15bd8fbd5746dfc53b0687254f4ee3a7","tid":658612,"uid":2896,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T06:46:57.000Z","msg":"單手捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c011b4071c85115e7611abede706fb7b92d8b7ae","tid":658612,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T06:47:32.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/20180205115415_5a77d56780d66_8032811535aec47558325a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F20180205115415_5a77d56780d66_8032811535aec47558325a.jpg&h=7a84f1f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蚊子上下移動的速度較快<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/20180205115443_5a77d5831fc4a_7366495745aec47783d200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F20180205115443_5a77d5831fc4a_7366495745aec47783d200.jpg&h=7eead32d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蚊子左右移動的速度相對較慢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/20180205115341_5a77d5455ccbd_17326948155aec479354a23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F20180205115341_5a77d5455ccbd_17326948155aec479354a23.jpg&h=afacab57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正確打蚊方法是雙手要由上、下方拍</span></div>"},{"pid":"d1d7483f8aea40b40369a52f5fbe39a332cb9b48","tid":658612,"uid":56240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T06:48:26.000Z","msg":"寧願學防蚊"},{"pid":"a6e19d232668e49ca83ab23b467a1b41d155d602","tid":658612,"uid":83328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T06:49:52.000Z","msg":"一拳超人唯一殺唔死嘅對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}